  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Apply global trade compliance and sanction screening.]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: AutoML - Determine compliant environmental practices for parts and packaging.]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: RCA Service - Investigate quality defects in service parts.]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Ensure safety and emissions compliance for parts.]
  N5 --> N6[Cortex: AutoML - Implement measures to detect and prevent counterfeit parts.]
  N6 --> N7{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Present AI recommendations for compliance actions.}
  N7 -->|Primary| N8[PB: Remote Functions - Execute remediation actions and update SAP S/4HANA.]
  N8 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS from defects, improved working capital through faster issue resolution, and mitigated compliance risk across the service parts network.]
  N7 -->|Non-compliant trade practice detected.| B1[Initiate CWB Lifecycle for manual review and override.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Manual intervention to adjust compliance actions.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Significant quality defect identified.| B2[Trigger RCA Service for detailed investigation.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Detailed root cause analysis and remediation plan.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Potential counterfeit part detected.| B3[Activate AutoML for advanced detection and prevention.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Enhanced counterfeit prevention measures implemented.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]